this project is creating for checking the deployment feature by using the adding war file with different versions.
the procedure im using now is 
create one war file
push files to git
build the war file with jenkins
create one tomcat image in docker and deploy war file in it. 


some useful commands for k8s testing

 scp -i jenkins.pem /var/lib/jenkins/workspace/k8s/target/linux.war ubuntu@44.202.161.179:/home/ubuntu

 sudo docker cp /home/ubuntu/linux.war ae58824ff120:/usr/local/tomcat/webapps

